ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (NAATS'IHCH'OH NATIONAL PARK RESERVE) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal the surface and subsurface rights of certain lands (approximately 7,600 km²) located within the South Nahanni Headwaters of the Sahtu Settlement Area, in the Northwest Territories, in order facilitate the settlement of the Nááts'ihch'oh National Park Reserve.
